WEBVTT

00:00.280 --> 00:01.240
How mean.

00:01.530 --> 00:03.450
Writing graffiti on my desk.

00:04.220 --> 00:07.060
As usual, Kyoko-chan won’t say anything to me.

00:07.800 --> 00:10.260
I didn’t do that.

00:10.840 --> 00:13.140
I’ve never gone out with Tomo-kun.

00:13.940 --> 00:15.960
I felt like everyone was mocking me.

00:16.560 --> 00:18.480
I don’t want to go to school anymore.
